Name: medialog.newsitemview
Version: 0.9
Summary: Set size of image for newsitem and folder_contents
Home-page: http://products.medialog.no
Author: Grieg Medialog [Espen Moe-Nilssen]
Author-email: espen@medialog.no
License: GPL
Description: ------------
        Introduction
        ------------
        
        
        `medialog.newsitemview` is a simple package that adds an option to choose size of newitem image, both in newsitem-view and summary view.
        It also has an option to hide images from summary view.
        
        See http://products.medialog.no/newsitem-view/
        
        .. image:: http://products.medialog.no/Skjermbilde20111115kl.17.29.57.png
               
        ----
                
